{{纳吉系列}}
'''纳-{}-吉'''（{{bd|1953年|7月23日|catIdx=A}}）全名为'''莫哈末·纳-{}-吉·阿-{}-都-{}-拉-{}-萨'''（{{lang-ms|Mohd Najib bin Abdul Razak}}）
全名加上头銜全称为'''[[马来西亚封衔|拿督斯里]][[哈芝|哈芝]]莫哈末·纳吉·[[敦_(头衔)|敦]][[哈芝|哈芝]]阿都拉萨'''（{{lang|ms|Dato' Sri Haji Mohammad Najib bin Tun Haji Abdul Razak}}），[[馬來民族統一機構|巫统]][[北根国会议席|北根区]]国会议员，曾是[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]第六任[[马来西亚首相|首相]]。他也是一名具争议的政治领袖，于2020年因[[一个马来西亚发展有限公司丑闻|一个马来西亚发展有限公司丑闻]]（1MDB）被定罪<ref>{{Cite news|title=Najib Razak, Malaysia’s Former Prime Minister, Found Guilty in Graft Trial|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/28/world/asia/malaysia-1mdb-najib.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-07-28|accessdate=2021-12-10|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Richard C.|last=Paddock|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227162915/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/28/world/asia/malaysia-1mdb-najib.html}}</ref>。

纳吉曾于2004年至2009年担任[[马来西亚副首相|马来西亚副首相]]，在任期间他曾被指控参与了2006年[[阿尔丹杜雅·沙丽布谋杀案|阿尔丹杜雅·沙丽布谋杀案]]（Altantuya Shaariibuu）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Altantuya: Razak's PI makes shocking statutory declaration (Update)|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2008/07/03/altantuya-razaks-pi-makes-shocking-statutory-declaration-update|access-date=2021-07-06|last=HABIB|first=SHAHANAAZ|work=The Star|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423212826/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2008/07/03/altantuya-razaks-pi-makes-shocking-statutory-declaration-update}}</ref>，但他否认涉及该案。2009年4月3日，纳吉在[[国家皇宫_(吉隆坡)|国家皇宫]]正式宣誓就职，成为马来西亚第六任首相。

2011年8月31日[[马来西亚独立日|马来西亚国庆日]]，纳吉前往[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]度假引起争议<ref name="cctvat"/>。[[2013年马来西亚大选|2013年大选]]连任后他的政府开始对批评者以煽动罪名提控，以[[肛交|肛交案]]审讯监禁反对党领袖[[安华·依布拉欣|安华·依布拉欣]]，实行[[消费税|消费税]]，涉入[[一個馬來西亞發展有限公司|一个马来西亚发展有限公司丑闻]]风波导致一系列由草根组织净选盟发动要求纳吉下台的抗议集会<ref>[http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/arrests-at-rally-calling-for-najibs-resignation Arrests at rally calling for Najib's resignation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/arrests-at-rally-calling-for-najibs-resignation |date=20150806013210 }}. The Straits Times, 1 August 2015. Retrieved 25 August 2015.</ref><ref>[https://www.wsj.com/articles/protesters-call-on-malaysian-prime-minister-to-resign-1438437489 Protesters Call on Malaysian Prime Minister to resign] {{Wayback|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/protesters-call-on-malaysian-prime-minister-to-resign-1438437489 |date=20170831215050 }}. The Wall Street Journal, 1 August 2015. Retrieved 25 August 2015.</ref><ref>[http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/bersih-plans-overnight-rally-in-august-to-demand-najibs-resignation Bersih plans overnight rally in August to demand Najib's resignation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/bersih-plans-overnight-rally-in-august-to-demand-najibs-resignation |date=20150826222429 }}. The Straits Times, 29 July 2015. Retrieved 25 August 2015.</ref>。这些抗议集会最终促成了由[[马哈迪·莫哈末|马哈迪·莫哈末]]和[[希望聯盟|希望联盟]]以及非政府组织组成的《[[马来西亚公民宣言|公民宣言]]》，以使他下台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/malaysia-alliance-demands/2572686.html|title=Malaysia alliance demands removal of scandal-hit PM Najib|accessdate=2016-09-09|publisher=|archive-date=2016-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712144352/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/malaysia-alliance-demands/2572686.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/mahathir-and-opposition-sign-declaration-to-oust-najib|title=Malaysia's Mahathir and opposition sign declaration to oust Najib|accessdate=2016-09-09|date=2016-03-04|last=hermesauto|first=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329195113/https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/mahathir-and-opposition-sign-declaration-to-oust-najib|dead-url=no}}</ref>。纳吉对贪腐指控的回应是集中权力，撤换副首相及总检察长，起诉发表一马公司相关言论的[[馬來西亞華人公會|马华公会]]前总会长[[林良实|林良实]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=入禀高庭要求赔偿 纳吉起诉林良实诽谤 中国报|url=http://www.chinapress.com.my/20151029/%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%AD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E7%B4%8D%E5%90%89%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E5%AF%A6%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97/?variant=zh-hans|access-date=2021-09-04|work=中国报 China Press|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206041614/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20151029/%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%AD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E7%B4%8D%E5%90%89%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E5%AF%A6%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97/?variant=zh-hans}}</ref>，冻结两家报章出版及在国会通过争议的《国家安全委员会法令》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/malaysia-1mdb-najib-idUSL3N10L2P120150811#5Js2PtR7YiUo62fQ.97|title=Malaysia's Najib looks to ride out political crisis|accessdate=2015-12-08|date=2015-08-11|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329183751/https://www.reuters.com/article/malaysia-1mdb-najib-idUSL3N10L2P120150811#5Js2PtR7YiUo62fQ.97|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businesstimes.com.sg/government-economy/new-bill-gives-najib-extensive-powers|title=New bill gives Najib extensive powers|accessdate=2015-12-08|date=2015-12-05|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329200633/https://www.businesstimes.com.sg/government-economy/new-bill-gives-najib-extensive-powers|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[2018年马来西亚大选|2018年5月9日大选]]中，纳吉领导的国阵败选。5月12日，他与夫人[[罗斯玛·曼梳|罗斯玛·曼梳]]被[[马来西亚移民局|马来西亚移民局]]列入禁止出国的黑名单<ref>{{Cite web|title=纳吉夫妇被列入黑名单 遭移民局禁止出国  国内|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2018/05/12/242950|accessdate=2021-04-12|work=東方網 馬來西亞東方日報|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426214712/https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2018/05/12/242950}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=纳吉夫妇被列入黑名单 遭移民局禁止出国|url=https://news.seehua.com/?p=363271|accessdate=2021-04-12|date=2018-05-12|last=張|first=David|work=马来西亚诗华日报新闻网|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412133912/https://news.seehua.com/?p=363271}}</ref>。7月3日，纳吉在家中遭[[马来西亚反贪污委员会|马来西亚反贪污委员会]]逮捕<ref>{{Cite news|title=Malaysia’s Ex-Leader, Najib Razak, Is Charged in Corruption Inquiry|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/03/world/asia/najib-razak-arrested-malaysia.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2018-07-03|accessdate=2021-04-12|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Hannah|last=Beech|first2=Austin|last2=Ramzy|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226120420/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/03/world/asia/najib-razak-arrested-malaysia.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Former Malaysian PM Najib Razak arrested, to be charged on Wednesday over 1MDB scandal|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/najib-razak-arrested-1mdb-scandal-to-be-charged-10495160|accessdate=2021-04-12|work=CNA|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820211427/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/najib-razak-arrested-1mdb-scandal-to-be-charged-10495160}}</ref>，7月4日被控3项SRC资金失信控状及一项贪污滥权控状，涉嫌款项为4200万令吉<ref>{{Cite web|title=控状速译中文版！纳吉被控4条罪|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/20180704/%e6%8e%a7%e7%8a%b6%e9%80%9f%e8%af%91%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%87%e7%89%88%ef%bc%81%e7%ba%b3%e5%90%89%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%a74%e6%9d%a1%e7%bd%aa/|access-date=|date=2018-07-04|work=星洲网 Sin Chew Daily|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422081103/https://www.sinchew.com.my/20180704/%e6%8e%a7%e7%8a%b6%e9%80%9f%e8%af%91%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%87%e7%89%88%ef%bc%81%e7%ba%b3%e5%90%89%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%a74%e6%9d%a1%e7%bd%aa/}}</ref>。8月8日，纳吉再被控3项涉嫌相同款项的洗黑钱控状<ref>{{Cite web|title=非法收取SRC的4200万，纳吉被加控三宗罪|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/437982|access-date=|date=2018-08-08|last=马新社|work=Malaysiakini|archive-date=2022-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418113522/https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/437982}}</ref>。森美兰和雪兰莪的皇室也相继宣布褫夺他的“[[拿督斯里|拿督斯里]]”头衔<ref>{{Cite web|title=维护森州王室名誉 收回纳吉夫妇勋衔|url=https://www.cincainews.com/news/malaysia/2018/10/26/20181026-negri-palace-strips-najib-rosmah-of-awards/1686918|access-date=|date=2018-10-26|last=综合报导|work=精彩大马|language=zh|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422081115/https://www.cincainews.com/news/malaysia/2018/10/26/20181026-negri-palace-strips-najib-rosmah-of-awards/1686918}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=雪苏丹冻结纳吉夫妇封勋 直至各自面控案审结|url=https://www.themalaysianinsight.com/index.php/chinese/s/153600|access-date=|date=2019-05-10|work=www.themalaysianinsight.com|language=zh|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422081105/https://www.themalaysianinsight.com/index.php/chinese/s/153600}}</ref>。

