===马来西亚国防部长（1999年至2008年）===
纳吉担任[[马来西亚国防部|马来西亚国防部长]]期间于2003年12月提出了强制军事服务计划<ref>[http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Southeast_Asia/FE04Ae01.html Malaysia's 3-month national service a flop?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Southeast_Asia/FE04Ae01.html |date=20081123095047 }}, Asia Times Online, 4 May 2004</ref>。计划开始后的首五年，超过339000位马来西亚青年参与了国民服务计划（PLKN）<ref>[http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2008/5/16/parliament/21270333&sec=parliament RM2.37bil spent on NS] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080518014125/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2008%2F5%2F16%2Fparliament%2F21270333&sec=parliament |date=2008-05-18 }}, The Star, 16 May 2008</ref>，但该计划一直都管理不善，截至2008年5月已有16人在该计划中丧生<ref>[http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2008/05/11/asia/AS-GEN-Malaysia-National-Service.php Malaysian family to sue government over daughter's death during national service] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2008/05/11/asia/AS-GEN-Malaysia-National-Service.php |date=20080520233240 }}, Associated Press, 11 May 2008</ref><ref>[http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v3/printable.php?id=283499 Government Won't Compromise On Negligence At NS Training Camps] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v3/printable.php?id=283499 |date=20071025101205 }}, Bernama, 6 September 2007.</ref>。

