8/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20180223/%E7%B4%8D%E5%90%89%E5%90%83%E8%97%9C%E9%BA%A5%E6%83%B9%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E9%A6%AC%E5%93%88%E8%BF%AA%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AA%E5%90%83%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%99%BD%E7%B1%B3/amp/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=敦馬臉書諷納吉吃藜麥 “我只吃本地米”|url=https://guangming.com.my/%e6%95%a6%e9%a6%ac%e8%87%89%e6%9b%b8%e8%ab%b7%e7%b4%8d%e5%90%89%e5%90%83%e8%97%9c%e9%ba%a5-%e6%88%91%e5%8f%aa%e5%90%83%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0%e7%b1%b3|accessdate=2021-02-25|work=光明日报|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426220505/https://guangming.com.my/%E6%95%A6%E9%A6%AC%E8%87%89%E6%9B%B8%E8%AB%B7%E7%B4%8D%E5%90%89%E5%90%83%E8%97%9C%E9%BA%A5-%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AA%E5%90%83%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%B1%B3}}</ref>[[民主行动党_(马来西亚)|民主行动党]]元老[[林吉祥|林吉祥]]指出，纳吉吃的藜麦，比3000万名大马人平日吃的白米贵23倍，明显与人民的困苦脱节<ref>{{Cite web|title=林吉祥：纳吉吃藜麦比白米贵23倍|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2018/02/23/232779|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=東方網 馬來西亞東方日報|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426220441/https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2018/02/23/232779}}</ref>，《[[南洋商报|南洋商报]]》也报导指“藜麦”成为了马来西亚[[Google|谷歌]]用户热搜的关键词<ref>{{Cite web|title=“藜麦”成大马谷歌热搜词|url=https://www.enanyang.my/node/141868|access-date=2021-12-28|date=2018-02-23|work=www.enanyang.my|language=zh-hans}}</ref>。

